{"commentv2": 1, "number": 25, "id": 551757, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "299389", "body": "I've been soloing him for a while as a lvl 80 feral druid with tank spec. My gear is a mix between some heroic pieces, quest rewards and crafted things like Polar Boots and so. Unfortunately the mount hasn't drop yet.\n\nI read on another web page that it is also soleable for resto druids so I supose that boomkins can do it too but don't spend the entire battle HoTing the statues because this way you will lose the loot, simply finish Anzu when he is at 5k Hp or so. Good luck!", "date": "2009-01-07T16:21:23-06:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2009-01-07T16:21:53-06:00", 1, "299389"]}
