{"commentv2": 1, "number": 33, "id": 694508, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Iceburgh69", "body": "Ok. For me, I'm fully Naxx 25-geared, Feral DPS specced and geared. I'd try to heal, even out of LOS, and I'd get bombed. No heals get through and I lose mana, of which I have precious little. I died 4 times before even summoning the boss (twice before even making it into the room), 2-3 times on my way BACK to the boss, and probably another half-dozen times on the boss himself. I don't know if it's bugged or not, but I'm trying it again later with a Druid healer. With my heals getting stopped, including Rejuve and Lifebloom, I can't solo him.\r\n\r\nAlso, he summons his adds and Banishes at 75% for me.", "date": "2009-04-26T06:53:09-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
