{"commentv2": 1, "number": 55, "id": 885681, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "105902", "body": "I've started a farm for this guy on my warrior. Here's how:\r\nStealth in with the lvl 80 druid i have laying around, summon boss.. have a friend standing inside the instance, so that when i log on my warrior and enter, it's the same instance id. \r\nIt takes a bit more time than a stealthing druid, but you can bypass most of the packs purely by being lvl 80. Being nightelf is a bonus for shadowmeld as well.", "date": "2009-11-08T07:07:06-06:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 56, "id": 886967, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "kri4o", "body": "Well guys, I've been wanting this mount ever since I saw someone with it, I've seen it drop 6 times and lost it 6 times. What else can I say?\r\n\r\nI believe this is soloable by a lvl 80 frost mage, I tried today, but failed, although I still believe its doable.\r\n\r\nMy mage is a level 80 Human Mage, Elliza on Burning Legion EU. Feel free to check out my spec(a pvp spec, not for Anzu farming :p) and gear.\r\n\r\nWhat I did was, I used Mirror Images, Water Elemental popped Icy Veins and started nuking as hard as I could. Got him in the first banish phase quite easily. Images died so did the elemental. You might wanna slow down the add killing so you can have your images off cooldown after he goes out of the second banish phase, otherwise you die without anything to divert his attention from you. After banish phase, pop Cold Snap, use elemental and Icy veins again. Nuke to 2nd banish phase, evocate, bandage pot/gem if needed (I use glyph of evocation). Again wait a bit for images to recharge. If he starts casting Paralyzing Screech, pop Ice Block so you don't get unwanted dmg. After he exits 2nd banish phase, pop images and hope you don't die. Nuke hard and try to avoid being near him when hes killing your images. Don't forget to remove curse.\r\n\r\nI'll post an update when I get him down. Good luck and keep trying.\r\n\r\n(Soloing this because I cba to pay some1 for help or pay 1k gold to some1 for a summon, I usually pay 20g which is reasonable if I can solo him.)", "date": "2009-11-09T18:17:50-06:00", "rating": -3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 57, "id": 907048, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "DeadMAX", "body": "1. try: Boomkin 5/5 T9,5 - died on 55% - crits for 6,5k and 6k...\r\n2. try: Tree (pve resto with bonus armor talent), downed in 7 minutes - keeping up all spirits and doing dps with glyphed and talented barskin....just decursing mana bomb and using innervate on cd...not so easy but doable.", "date": "2009-12-05T14:58:06-06:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
