{"commentv2": 1, "number": 63, "id": 947976, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Lythiaren", "body": "A tip for those who have their mounts already and are helping others to farm him: assuming you're both 80s, you don't need to clear through the instance.  After 82 tries, I've gotten the reins for a shadow priest friend.  Here's how we've been doing it:\r\n\r\n1. Buff up and clear the entrance hallway.\r\n2. Position your friend in that hole in the middle of the floor in the first room.  If the trash pull to the right of the door has a habit of jumping your buddy on the way, I recommend clearing that pull before your friend goes to sit in the hole.\r\n3. Stealth through the instance, directly to [b]Ikiss[/b].\r\n4. Make war on Ikiss, opening the shortcut and allowing your friend to come up and join you.\r\n5. Backtrack through Anzu's room to clear trash; it's faster and easier with two people, especially if one can break fear on the other.  Put the moonstone in just before you pull the last pull and kite them behind the box in the corner, he will be about done talking by the time you've cleared the last pull.\r\n6. Kick Anzu in the face, cross fingers for reins.\r\n\r\nEach run took me about 20 minutes between initial buffing and my frustrated war stomp on his corpse when he gave us yet another boomstick or talon.  By the time we saw the reins again, I'd gotten so used to the instance that I was starting to clear the trash out of the room 2 pulls at a time.  I don't recommend this unless you're at least Naxx25/U10 geared.", "date": "2010-01-15T08:13:19-06:00", "rating": 8, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "82 tries??? For that mount? WOW!", "creationdate": "2016-01-02T11:31:30-06:00", "id": 922360, "rating": 0, "commentid": 947976, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "shariff666", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
