{"commentv2": 1, "number": 67, "id": 996984, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "314557", "body": "Very easy solo as a moonkin in ICC gear.\r\n\r\nFor the trash, root one add, hibernate if there's a bird. Trash should be fairly easy. Cyclone if you need it to stop some damage. \r\n\r\nFor the boss, I pre-hotted myself and nuked him to the first banish phase. I re-hotted myself before the adds came, then went back to moonkin, ate the stun, then hurricaned them down. Hotted myself again as Anzu ran back to me. Used treants/starfall to push him to banish again quickly. Rehotted + innervated before the second pack came down, then aoe'd them down. Rehot one more time before he comes over for 33%-0. I was never remotely close to being in danger of death. I cast regrowths on each of the bird spirits before I pulled, but I doubt it was necessary. I also did not trinket any of his stuns.", "date": "2010-03-13T21:31:47-06:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 68, "id": 1024006, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "WardenKhan", "body": "I did this at Resto druid, full PvE gear and PvE spec, very easy. I cleared the room summoned Anzu hotted up and moonfire spam. Deadly boss mods is very useful for Paralyzing Screech, during that I used barkskin. and you can dispel the spell bomb decursive helps here.", "date": "2010-04-21T20:46:52-05:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
