{"commentv2": 1, "number": 84, "id": 1141620, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "251368", "body": "After the implementation of patch 4.0.1 last night, I finally soloed him with ease as moonkin spec after multiple tries resulting in failure. The only problem is.. The quest to defeat him seems to be disappearing from my quest log every time I zone in. When I downed Anzu I hadn't noticed :-( seems to be a bug in the new patch and hopefully will be fixed soon", "date": "2010-10-13T13:05:32-05:00", "rating": -3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "They fixed the bug.  Alas, the \"fix\" is that Morthis no longer offers the quest.  (The reason it was disappearing on logout or zoning was that it's in the list of removed quests.  The fact that Morthis was still offering it was the bug.)", "creationdate": "2010-10-16T00:22:14-05:00", "id": 460548, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1141620, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "362863", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
