{"commentv2": 1, "number": 86, "id": 1143155, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "680057", "body": "As of 4.0.1, you no longer need a druid with a Essence-Infused Moonstone to summon Anzu. \r\nHe is also easy to solo for a level 80 Death Knight.", "date": "2010-10-15T05:06:26-05:00", "rating": 77, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "[b]I can 100% confirm the [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=32768]Anzu mount[/url] still drops from Anzu on US realms.[/b] HAPPY FARMING EVERYONE! [b]:D[/b]", "creationdate": "2010-10-15T14:11:01-05:00", "id": 186777, "rating": 15, "commentid": 1143155, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "tmptfate", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Hunters using bears as tanking pets will find this boss slow to take down, but super easy.", "creationdate": "2010-10-16T11:45:13-05:00", "id": 460587, "rating": -4, "commentid": 1143155, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "kasuturo", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "yeah i can confirm, anzu is stupid easy to solo as a blood DK.  Just DND and blood boil the adds and wail on the boss when u can. Easy easy tank and spank.", "creationdate": "2010-10-16T16:36:50-05:00", "id": 460605, "rating": -4, "commentid": 1143155, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "malminos", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
