{"commentv2": 1, "number": 90, "id": 1143748, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "c0h3n", "body": "I just ran H Seth today and to my surprise Anzu was spawned with the room empty of trash. Additionally The final pull before the final boss was removed as well. Either Blizzard changed it so you no longer require a druid that has completed Swift Flight Form quest to summon Anzu, or I experienced a very odd glitch. Due to the removal of trash, I'm inclined to believe this was intentional.", "date": "2010-10-15T19:27:22-05:00", "rating": -3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I can confirm that this is the case. I ran Heroic Sethekk today and Anzu was spawned upon zoning in, and no trash is in his room.", "creationdate": "2010-10-15T19:44:27-05:00", "id": 460541, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1143748, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Ushikawa", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
