{"commentv2": 1, "number": 165, "id": 1587667, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "Boomkeen", "body": "I went into the dungeon on heroic mode and couldn't summon Anzu. :( Do you need a druid again or what?", "date": "2011-12-02T23:37:03-06:00", "rating": -6, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I found that the first time I entered, even though it said it was heroic, and had the heroic portal... it wasn't. I re-did all the quests from the new givers, left, reset, and re-entered and it was actually heroic the second time.", "creationdate": "2011-12-04T19:35:22-06:00", "id": 283225, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1587667, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Medlir", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I reset and it was still normal...even with the skull on the portal.", "creationdate": "2012-04-22T04:08:46-05:00", "id": 537705, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1587667, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "luinel", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 166, "id": 1589682, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Medlir", "body": "I just tried to do him for the 61st time, and he's not there in 4.3.  Saw the new in-dungeon quests givers who gave me quests I already had done.  And then got to his room, all trash... looked at my difficulty... heroic.  Even verified the portal texture was a skull when I left.  If he's gone for real, I'll be a sad panda.\n\nEdit:\n\nOkay, I don't know if it has to do with how they changed the dungeons, but as I said, I had verified it was set to heroic in both the menu and the portal texture from the inside was the skull.  But I left, it let me reset, and re-enter, and do it again and it was fine the second time.  Not sure what the deal is.", "date": "2011-12-04T19:23:27-06:00", "rating": -6, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2011-12-04T19:34:22-06:00", 1, "Medlir"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 167, "id": 1592452, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "327123", "body": "Been running this every day for months on hunter.  Anzu was always there, but mount never dropped.  Then ran it on druid and it dropped the first run.  Now Anzu isn't even there on (85) hunter (in heroic mode).  The room is filled with mobs, but no Anzu.  What happened?", "date": "2011-12-08T05:45:40-06:00", "rating": -5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Perhaps you have the same problem Mediir did (see comment just before yours). I just ran it (literally just, I'm posting this after having finished) and Anzu was there - might need a shuffling of dungeon modes or something.", "creationdate": "2011-12-09T04:21:22-06:00", "id": 285448, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1592452, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Ulgoth", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 168, "id": 1595131, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "jquintel", "body": "I can confirm what has been said, ran in on heroic, easily burning down mobs, got to Anzu wasn't there. Went back out, reset instance, set to normal, then back to heroic, and went back in, and he was there.", "date": "2011-12-12T19:03:24-06:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 169, "id": 1598613, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Palatrino", "body": "Finally! I got the mount to drop today, feels like an early Christmas gift! :D\r\n\r\nIf you're still around 40-50 and feel like it's never dropping, I did around 160 kills before it dropped so I know how it can feel. Just kill him every single day even though you hate the instance more than anything, and eventually it will drop. It worked for me! (I think I managed getting the runs down to  ~2-3min which isn't much per day)\r\n\r\nI'm not ever putting my foot into Sethekk Halls again though, that's for sure... ^^\r\n\r\n------------------------------------\r\n\r\n[i]Tip. Put your HS in Shattrath City, since there's a portal to either Orgrimmar or Stormwind in the middle of the city. Plus there's way less people and you have auction house there anyways so you're not really missing anything out. Therefore, there's no excuse not going to Sethekk Ba...eh Halls [u]every single day![/u][/i]\r\n\r\n//Palatrino", "date": "2011-12-18T22:50:55-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 170, "id": 1605457, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Emma8Night", "body": "For some reason the mobs aren't cleared out, and Anzu is not there. \nI've run the place a few times hoping to kill the guy (Nope). Sigh...\nQuick Facts:\n\nI am not in a group.\n\nI know I have it on Heroic (maybe not right kind?).\n\nI know which room he is in (the one right before Ikiss, has a blue tinge to the room on the map).\n\nLooking for possible solutions, please.", "date": "2012-01-01T21:56:40-06:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "This is due to a bug where you can be shown the heroic \"skull\" entrance, yet still end up in the normal mode dungeon. I'm not sure what triggers it, but it has happened to me while in a raid group. Try swapping your difficulty back and forth and you should be able to go get into the heroic version just fine.", "creationdate": "2012-01-19T02:39:55-06:00", "id": 509633, "rating": 3, "commentid": 1605457, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "silthania", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2012-01-06T18:58:35-06:00", 4, "Emma8Night"]}
