{"commentv2": 1, "number": 175, "id": 1624176, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "892882", "body": "How do you summon anzu? By clicking an orb or something\r\nI want to farm it on my 85 hunter but i have never done this boss before", "date": "2012-02-09T16:36:39-06:00", "rating": -5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Anzu is no longer summoned by the orb. Just get to the room where he is found on heroic mode and he should be there", "creationdate": "2012-05-07T14:48:44-05:00", "id": 541844, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1624176, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "360595", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
