{"commentv2": 1, "number": 177, "id": 1626754, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "930287", "body": "Im an 85. how do I change the dungeon to heroic mode? or is there some part i miss? I want to kill this boss. for the drop lol.", "date": "2012-02-15T02:34:07-06:00", "rating": -6, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Right click your portrait and select dungeon difficulty, then set it to heroic", "creationdate": "2012-05-07T14:47:52-05:00", "id": 541843, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1626754, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "360595", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 178, "id": 1628219, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "235370", "body": "Farming the Mount has pretty much become a Daily with my own personal Achievement.\r\n\r\nSo far I managed to get him on 6 Characters but despite my greatest efforts I'm not able to down him before he manages to cast his ( uber annoying ) self Banish at least once.\r\n\r\nThe best so far was a 1% attempt with my Arcane Mage bombing the Nether out of him using [URL=http://www.wowhead.com/spell=80353]Time Warp[/URL], [URL=http://www.wowhead.com/spell=12042]Arane Power[/URL], [URL=http://www.wowhead.com/spell=55342]Mirror Image[/URL] and [URL=http://www.wowhead.com/spell=30451]Arcane Blast[/URL] in which he then dropped the Mount.\r\n\r\nAnzu must have feared me returning once more with better gear so he probably just gave in.\r\n\r\nAnyway... If you can you should try to get the awesome mount from him which shouldn't take more than 10min a day.\r\nIf you're still in the early 80s I do recommend to kill [URL=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=18473]Talon King Ikiss[/URL] first so you can enter from the exit in case of a whipe.", "date": "2012-02-17T20:02:43-06:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
