{"commentv2": 1, "number": 202, "id": 3206241, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "Myebika", "body": "For those looking to tame Anzu, go tame [url=https://www.wowhead.com/npc=41084/blaithe]Blaithe[/url] instead, he's a little ways into the Hyjal questline, near Aviana's nest, for the quest [url=https://www.wowhead.com/quest=25664/a-prayer-and-a-wing]A prayer and a wing.[/url]", "date": "2020-05-13T11:17:43-05:00", "rating": -4, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Already done the quest years ago, I have no friends that play wow and I'm currently in no guild because I'm a filthy casual so not being able to tame Anzu sucks as blaithe is now out of the question. GJ blizz", "creationdate": "2020-06-15T10:06:03-05:00", "id": 1374804, "rating": 1, "commentid": 3206241, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "biggaz69", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I found a very nice person on the forums that summoned Blaithe for me so I could tame. The forums are your friend! Here's the link to the thread. (https://us.forums.blizzard.com/en/wow/t/anzu-is-not-tamable/434409/17) Hunters are still posting on it!", "creationdate": "2020-07-09T19:43:52-05:00", "id": 1378519, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3206241, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "yellowpaine", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 203, "id": 3212660, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "biggaz69", "body": "Ok so I've found a way to tame blaithe solo even if you've already completed the quest. All credit goes to Foxinhound US realm Thrall:\r\n\r\nSteps\r\n\r\nHave your alt, in my case my rogue get to the quest.\r\n\r\nGo to group finder on your hunter and create a group name it something easy like mmm\r\n\r\nSwap back to your alt and find the group an apply\r\n\r\nLog back onto the hunter and invite, go back to alt to accept (convoluted I know).\r\n\r\nIMPORTANT WARNING! The NEST you use is important due to Phasing issues.\r\nI Used the nest located at (49.79, 41.59)\r\n\r\nHave your alt summon the bird, then either jump off the mountain, run away, or in my rogue\u2019s case just vanish. This will reset him allowing for a tame.\r\n\r\nQuickly log off and onto your hunter.\r\n\r\nIt worked for me hope this helps you.\r\n\r\nAnd this worked for me too.", "date": "2020-06-15T20:01:15-05:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 204, "id": 3220122, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "sw1fterly", "body": "Anzu currently IS tameable as beast lore says! Today I ran Sethekk Halls and decided to try and tame him for the heck of it, not expecting anything to happen because I remembered reading it didn't work. But the tame went through just fine! He retains his name after taming. Also, taming him doesn't remove or defeat the boss. A moment after taming, Anzu the boss respawned and I was able to kill and loot him.\r\n\r\nMaybe they fixed the issue in one of the recent hotfix patches? I will try to add a screenshot later.", "date": "2020-07-29T19:36:59-05:00", "rating": 10, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Aug 2020: just tamed Anzu (I'm level 120), no respawn.", "creationdate": "2020-09-19T11:27:11-05:00", "id": 1390859, "rating": 2, "commentid": 3220122, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "squiretoad", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Tamed him today, counted as having defeated him. Postmaster sent me the loot as if I had killed him.", "creationdate": "2020-11-07T22:11:01-06:00", "id": 1403878, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3220122, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Nynnaeve", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Confirming: You will have to wait for heroics to reset to tame a second one. As the previous two commenters have...commented, he did not respawn and loot came from the Postmaster. To remove any doubts, the Adventure Journal also marked him as dead.", "creationdate": "2020-12-14T17:21:48-06:00", "id": 1426151, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3220122, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Caedars", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
