{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 2048476, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "flepser", "body": "[quote]A mysterious avian deity worshipped by some of the more savage Arrakoa, Anzu is a being whose origins and powers are unlike any other member of Outland's fallen pantheon. The Naaru are silent regarding this malevolent creature, for Anzu's ways are hidden from even them.[/quote]\n\nHe might be friendly now, but when doing the druid swift flight form quest chain he was a major pain in the ass!", "date": "2014-11-25T10:19:33-06:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2014-11-25T10:20:02-06:00", 1, "flepser"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 2006420, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Souwx", "body": "I can only imagine the reaction he will have when I approach him with my Raven Lord mount.", "date": "2014-09-27T18:34:24-05:00", "rating": 23, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Let's not mention the fact that we farmed him on our timeline for weeks on end for the chance to ride him either. ; )", "creationdate": "2014-12-14T03:20:01-06:00", "id": 812568, "rating": 3, "commentid": 2006420, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "yoshimario40", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 2048478, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "flepser", "body": "[quote]A mysterious avian deity worshipped by some of the more savage arrakoa, Anzu is a being whose origins and powers are unlike any other member of Outland's fallen pantheon. The Naaru are silent regarding this malevolent creature, for Anzu's ways are hidden from even them.[/quote]\r\n\r\nFriendly now, but caused some major setbacks when doing the Druid swift flight form quest.", "date": "2014-11-25T10:21:06-06:00", "rating": 6, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "As revealed in one of Anzu's quests here in the Spires, the Sethekk are trying to dominate his will and have him spread darkness across Draenor. It stands to reason, then, that that's what happened in the main timeline without us to stop it and that's why he was malicious in BC.", "creationdate": "2014-11-25T13:07:18-06:00", "id": 799319, "rating": 4, "commentid": 2048478, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Reignac", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 2148261, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Necropenguin", "body": "Curiously, an NPC instead of an object.\r\n\r\nThis [npc=86961] is a sword, from which can be looted [item=118241]. In order to obtain this, you must cross over to the Shadow Realm by drinking an [item=115463] at the Shrine to Terokk at the co-ordinates 57.0, 79.0 in [zone=6722]", "date": "2015-03-30T21:23:17-05:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 766471, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "evankimori", "body": "Can these mobs be targetted and tamed? I'm trying to verify the [url=http://petopia.brashendeavors.net/html/mobs/mob_broodofanzu.html]article[/url] on Petopia as to whether or not they can be tamed. They have a very nice skin, relative to the Druid Flight Form and I'm thinking they'd make a very nice pet for Hunters.", "date": "2009-07-03T08:59:00-05:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Yes they can be tamed, and they will be in the family carrion birds, not bird of prey like the other crows with the same skin. That make this bird a ferocity pet. Great choice for people that want a bird as dps pet, but dislike the looks of the vultures and condors.  I just tamed one, out of curiousity. Farmed honored with Lower City to be able to get into Sethekk Halls on my hunter alt. Engaged with my tanking pet and killed all birds except one when they spawned. When Anzu banished the second time I placed a freezing trap on the last bird, dismissed my tanking pet and tamed the bird.", "creationdate": "2011-01-24T08:12:42-06:00", "id": 218365, "rating": 1, "commentid": 766471, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "363043", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "you can ALWAYS get there.", "creationdate": "2013-07-25T11:35:10-05:00", "id": 680298, "rating": 0, "commentid": 766471, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Anevara", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 1328952, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "Eligin", "body": "I tamed this yesterday, and levelled it up to 84 before logging out. \nToday when I logged in, after the patch, he was a bird of prey. I made a ticket, but GM didn't know what was wrong.\nHe just asked me to try and level a new one up. \nHopefully it will work this time... I really want this one as a carrion bird.\n\nEdit. Nope. This one is fixed, will no longer be a carrion bird when you tame it. Too bad, I really liked this skin.", "date": "2011-02-09T16:03:33-06:00", "rating": 8, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "there are others that are tameable and they look like this and the site petopia says that this one is tameable", "creationdate": "2013-07-25T11:34:00-05:00", "id": 680297, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1328952, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Anevara", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Bird of Prey has such limited utility and Carrion Bird has a very nice, universally useful ability. Ashame they did this.", "creationdate": "2014-10-11T20:58:02-05:00", "id": 777990, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1328952, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Aliandrin", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2011-02-09T16:13:20-06:00", 2, "Eligin"]}
