{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 2035405, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "Starchy", "body": "Gives you [item=118694]. If you're heading east out of the Harvesting Pits (56.55, 26.59), you'll find a path off the left; if you're heading west down the road through Howling Crag, it'll be on your right. You'll see a big animal skull a few yards down it. Follow that path up and it'll wind up and around (like a lollipop) till you get to the statue.", "date": "2014-11-16T23:30:34-06:00", "rating": 17, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Thank you! Your description helped perfectly!", "creationdate": "2014-12-05T16:17:36-06:00", "id": 807188, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2035405, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "MiakaBaka", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Thank you. Upvoted. :)", "creationdate": "2015-09-14T12:07:17-05:00", "id": 898869, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2035405, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "TriesteHunter", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 2043311, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "najshu", "body": "I am very pleased to see that Blizzard brought these little rewards for exploration back in the game. I mean right, it's just a grey item - but it still makes you feel like you've been rewarded for taking the loop up the Howling Crag.\r\n\r\nWay to go!", "date": "2014-11-21T13:31:02-06:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
